120
00:12:18,612 --> 00:12:20,113
[SPEAKER_00]: Next slide.

121
00:12:21,994 --> 00:12:26,136
[SPEAKER_00]: So for any more information that you may need or questions, you can contact me.

122
00:12:26,656 --> 00:12:30,719
[SPEAKER_00]: My information's here, deevans at medford-ma.org.

123
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,881
[SPEAKER_00]: The city website is medfordma.org or preservedmedford.org.

